ease patches yourself or distribute applications on environments where an internet connection might not be available) Tauri can bundle the runtime files for you.</p><div class="theme-admonition theme-admonition-caution alert alert--warning admonition_LlT9"><div class="admonitionHeading_tbUL"><span class="admonitionIcon_kALy"><svg viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.893 1.5c-.183-.31-.52-.5-.887-.5s-.703.19-.886.5L.138 13.499a.98.98 0 0 0 0 1.001c.193.31.53.501.886.501h13.964c.367 0 .704-.19.877-.5a1.03 1.03 0 0 0 .01-1.002L8.893 1.5zm.133 11.497H6.987v-2.003h2.039v2.003zm0-3.004H6.987V5.987h2.039v4.006z"></path></svg></span>caution</div><div class="admonitionContent_S0QG"><p>Distributing a fixed WebView2 Runtime version increases the Windows Installer by around 180MB.</p></div></div><ol><li>Download the WebView2 fixed version runtime from <a href="https://developer.microsoft.com/en-us/microsoft-edge/webview2/#download-section" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Microsoft&#x27;s website</a>. Dans cet exemple, le nom du fichier t√©l√©charg√© est <code>Microsoft.WebView2.FixedVersionRuntime.98.0.1108.50.x64.cab</code></li><li>Extraire le fichier dans le dossier de Tauri :</li></ol><div class="language-powershell codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-background-color:#282c34;--prism-color:#ffffff"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-powershell codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#ffffff"><span class="token plain">Expand </span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#8dc891">.</span><span class="token plain">\Microsoft</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#8dc891">.</span><span class="token plain">WebView2</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#8dc891">.</span><span class="token plain">FixedVersionRuntime</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#8dc891">.</span><span class="tok