ler with the fixed WebView2 runtime.</li></ol><h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="ignorer-linstallation">Ignorer l&#x27;installation<a href="windows#ignorer-linstallation" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Ignorer l&#x27;installation" title="Direct link to Ignorer l&#x27;installation">‚Äã</a></h3><p>You can remove the WebView2 Runtime download check from the installer by setting <a href="../../api/config#webviewinstallmode">webviewInstallMode</a> to <code>skip</code>. Votre application ne fonctionnera pas si l&#x27;utilisateur n&#x27;a pas le runtime install√©.</p><div class="theme-admonition theme-admonition-warning alert alert--danger admonition_LlT9"><div class="admonitionHeading_tbUL"><span class="admonitionIcon_kALy"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.05.31c.81 2.17.41 3.38-.52 4.31C3.55 5.67 1.98 6.45.9 7.98c-1.45 2.05-1.7 6.53 3.53 7.7-2.2-1.16-2.67-4.52-.3-6.61-.61 2.03.53 3.33 1.94 2.86 1.39-.47 2.3.53 2.27 1.67-.02.78-.31 1.44-1.13 1.81 3.42-.59 4.78-3.42 4.78-5.56 0-2.84-2.53-3.22-1.25-5.61-1.52.13-2.03 1.13-1.89 2.75.09 1.08-1.02 1.8-1.86 1.33-.67-.41-.66-1.19-.06-1.78C8.18 5.31 8.68 2.45 5.05.32L5.03.3l.02.01z"></path></svg></span>danger</div><div class="admonitionContent_S0QG"><p>Your application WILL NOT work if the user does not have the runtime installed and won&#x27;t attempt to install it.</p></div></div><div class="language-json codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-background-color:#282c34;--prism-color:#ffffff"><div class="codeBlockTitle_Ktv7">tauri.config.json</div><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-json codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#ffffff"><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#8dc891">{</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#ffffff"><span class="token plain">  </span><span class="token property" style=