><h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="remplacer-le-code-dinstallation-par-un-fichier-wix-personnalis√©">Remplacer le code d&#x27;installation par un fichier WiX personnalis√©<a href="windows#remplacer-le-code-dinstallation-par-un-fichier-wix-personnalis√©" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Remplacer le code d&#x27;installation par un fichier WiX personnalis√©" title="Direct link to Remplacer le code d&#x27;installation par un fichier WiX personnalis√©">‚Äã</a></h3><p>The Windows Installer XML defined by Tauri is configured to work for the common use case of simple webview-based applications (you can find it <a href="https://github.com/tauri-apps/tauri/blob/dev/tooling/bundler/src/bundle/windows/templates/main.wxs" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">here</a>). It uses <a href="https://docs.rs/handlebars/latest/handlebars/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">handlebars</a> so the Tauri CLI can brand your installer according to your <code>tauri.conf.json</code> definition. If you need a completely different installer, a custom template file can be configured on <a href="../../api/config#wixconfig.template"><code>tauri.bundle.windows.wix.template</code></a>.</p><h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="√©tendre-linstallateur-avec-des-fragments-wix">√âtendre l&#x27;installateur avec des fragments WiX<a href="windows#√©tendre-linstallateur-avec-des-fragments-wix" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to √âtendre l&#x27;installateur avec des fragments WiX" title="Direct link to √âtendre l&#x27;installateur avec des fragments WiX">‚Äã</a></h3><p>A <a href="https://wixtoolset.org/documentation/manual/v3/xsd/wix/fragment.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">WiX fragment</a> is a container where you can configure almost everything offered by WiX. Dans cet exemple, nous allons d√©finir un fragment qui √©crit deux entr√©es de registre :</p><div class="language-xml codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-background-color:#282c34;--prism-color:#ffffff"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-xml codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#ffffff"><span class="token prolog" style="color:#999999">&lt;?xml version=&quot;1.0&quot; encoding=&quot;utf-8&quot;?&gt;</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#ffffff"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token tag punctuation" style="color:#8dc891">&lt;</span><span class="token tag" style="color:#fc929e">Wix</span><span class="token tag" style="color:#fc929e"> </span><span class="token tag attr-name" style="color:#c5a5c5">xmlns</span><span class="token tag attr-value punctuation attr-equals" style="color:#8dc891">=</span><span class="token tag attr-value punctuation" style="color:#8dc891">&quot;</span><span class="token tag attr-value" style="color:#8dc891">http://schemas.microsoft.com/wix/2006/wi</span><span class="token tag attr-value punctuation" style="color:#8dc891">&quot;</span><span class="token tag punctuation" style="color:#8dc891">&gt;</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#ffffff"><span class="token plain">  </span><span class="token tag punctuation" style="color:#8dc891">&lt;</span><span class="token tag" style="color:#fc929e">Fragment</span><span class="token tag punctuation" style="color:#8dc891">&gt;</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#ffffff"><span class="token plain">    </span><span class="token comment" style="color:#999999">&lt;!-- Ces entr√©es de Registre doivent √™tre install√©es</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#ffffff"><span class="token comment" style="color:#999999">         √† la machine de l‚Äôutilisateur --&gt;</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#ffffff"><span class="